  "content_html": "<div class=\"rich-text\"><h3 class=\"font_3 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:40px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">ElNet PQ GR Interference and electrical measurements</span></span></h3></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Elant PQ is certified by a testing laboratory to the exclusive Class A standard for measuring the quality of electricity.<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>Elant PQ enables the generation of EN50160 reports.<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>Allant PQ enables recording of waves in electrical events.<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>Has a sampling rate of 1600 samples per cycle 3 voltages + 4 currents<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>Has a measurement accuracy of 0.2% (0.1% by special order).<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>Data collection for 24 months (voltage, current, power factor, energy, THD and more..)<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>Measurement of leakage current and current in the zero line (4 current transformers)<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>Clock with foreign exchange rates.<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>Measuring harmonies up to the 64th harmony.<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>RS485 + TCP/IP communication channels are built into the device.<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>Support for MODBUS/BACNET communication protocols.<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>Programming 3 digital outputs including delay.<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>Huge high quality color screen (144X144).<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>Graphical wave display and 3D harmonics display.<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>Simple and easy panel installation in front of the electrical panel or on a DIN rail.<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>Internet TCP/IP communication, e-mail support and WEB surfing to the device using a browser.<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>Built-in fast data collection.<br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>Collection of up to 1000 alarms / events.</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">and more…</span></span></p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><h3 class=\"font_3 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-size:40px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Related products</span></span></h3></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:22px; text-align:center;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:22px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">Control Applications Ltd</span></span></span></span></p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">making contact</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"