  "rich_text": [
    "ElNet PQ GR Interference and electrical measurements",
    "Elant PQ is certified by a testing laboratory to the exclusive Class A standard for measuring the quality of electricity.\nElant PQ enables the generation of EN50160 reports.\nAllant PQ enables recording of waves in electrical events.\nHas a sampling rate of 1600 samples per cycle 3 voltages + 4 currents\nבעל דיוק מדידה 0.2% (0.1% בהזמנה מיוחדת).\nData collection for 24 months (voltage, current, power factor, energy, THD and more..)\nMeasurement of leakage current and current in the zero line (4 current transformers)\nClock with foreign exchange rates.\nMeasuring harmonies up to the 64th harmony.\nRS485 + TCP/IP communication channels are built into the device.\nSupport for MODBUS/BACNET communication protocols.\nProgramming 3 digital outputs including delay.\nHuge high quality color screen (144X144).\nGraphical wave display and 3D harmonics display.\nSimple and easy panel installation in front of the electrical panel or on a DIN rail.\nInternet TCP/IP communication, e-mail support and WEB surfing to the device using a browser.\nBuilt-in fast data collection.\nCollection of up to 1000 alarms / events.\nand more…",
    "Related Products",
    "Control Applications Ltd",
    "making contact\nPhone: +972-3-6474998\n​\nFax: +972-3-6474598\nEmail:\ncal@ddc.co.il",
    "opening hours\nControl Applications Ltd\nSunday - Thursday\n08:00 - 17:00",
    "Address\n25 Barzel Street, Tel Aviv\n6971035\nIsrael",
    "© Copyright - Control Applications Ltd"
